OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Fa few showers. Becoming dry this
OL,7,Fafternoon with any showers mostly
OL,8,Fdying out, some bright or sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping too.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then dry for a
OL,13,Ftime before thickening cloud brings
OL,14,Frain across all parts later in the
OL,15,Fnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FRain will mostly clear away
OL,18,Fthrough the morning, although some
OL,19,Flight rain lingering over the hills.
OL,20,FThen dry before further rain spreads
OL,21,Fnortheast in the evening. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
