OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and warm on Friday but rain likely
OL,7,Flater. Dry, bright and warm over the
OL,8,Fweekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
